////Lymph nodes, axillary

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 - Soft tissue of Shoulder MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lymph nodes, axillary' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Borderline LN, hilar fat preserved' radio button is enabled
And 'Lymphadenopathy' radio button is enabled
And 'Inflammation' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Borderline LN, hilar fat preserved' radio button
Then 'Short axis diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Lymphadenopathy' radio button
Then 'Short axis diameter' input field is enabled
